title: Questions For Taylor Swift!
description:
Taylor? Are you listening? The Swifties have come together and we all have questions for you!
We asked YOU what questions you have for Taylor herself, and we are adding them to our on-going list!
What else should we ask? And Taylor... Please let us know if you hear us!
